node.text: Small win this week for enthusiasts and the fight against the EPA's proposed ban on converting street cars into racecars and prohibiting selling/installing performance goods. If you haven't signed the RPM Act letter, please do so. If you have, please do so again. 1.5 million letters helped get this noticed, but it needs more support.
